<P>
Two ABC Wednesday-night, half-hour sitcoms will switch time periods this week, 
network officials announced. "Anything but Love," which stars Jamie Lee Curtis 
and Richard Lewis as colleagues at a Chicago magazine, was in a 9 p.m. slot. It 
