laugh at news conference. ; Photo, Former KGB generals Valentin Zvezdenkov, 
left, and Fjodor Sherbak chow down at RAND Corp. during first official visit by 
KGB officials to America. BRIAN GADBERY 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
