<DOCNO> LA100289-0069 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 115281 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 2, 1989, Monday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part 2; Page 1; Column 5; Metro Desk 
</P>
