<P>
BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
McKinsey May Buy High-Tech Firm: Management consulting firm McKinsey &amp; Co. 
is attempting to buy Information Consulting Group, a consulting company 
specializing in information technology and systems, for an undisclosed price, 
the New York Times reported. Saatchi &amp; Saatchi, the British advertising 
company that put up seed money for ICG when it was launched last year, also has 
an option to buy the firm, but earlier this year announced its intention to 
divest of its consulting operations to focus on advertising. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
