attempts to climb fence into West German Embassy in Prague. ; Photo, Long line 
for visas -- A new U.S. Embassy policy requiring that Soviet applications for 
visas be made in Moscow brought out about 16,000 to line up for application 
forms today. Associated Press 
</P>
