<TYPE>
<P>
Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA100289-0101 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 115401 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 2, 1989, Monday, P.M. Final 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 2; Column 1; Late Final Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
